**SmartGrid API**
- Added .NET 8 minimal Web API with in-memory seed data; `Program.cs` wires controllers and `InMemoryDatabase` singleton.
- Modeled 30 domain classes (incl. SolarFarm, WindTurbine, HydroPlant, BatteryStorage, SubstationMonitor, LoadBalancer, UsageBilling, etc.) in `SmartGrid.Api/Models/Entities.cs`.
- REST endpoints: power generation/PPAs/forecasts (`Controllers/PowerGenerationController.cs`), grid stability/faults/maintenance (`Controllers/GridStabilityController.cs`), and customer metering/billing/outages (`Controllers/CustomerMeteringController.cs`).
- SQL Server schema covering the same 30 entities saved at `SmartGrid.Api/Data/schema.sql`.
- Project scaffold & config in `SmartGrid.Api/SmartGrid.Api.csproj` with sample connection string in `SmartGrid.Api/appsettings.json`.

